public interface GISymbolicNameReference
extends GIReferenceToContainer
    Base interface of bswmd model references which point to a GIContainer and also have a parameter in the definition which is marked as SymbolcNameReference.
    SymbolicNameReferences have the same methods as GIReferenceToContainer and the additional methods getRefTargetParameterMdf(), which returns the target parameter as MIObject The method getRefTargetParameter() return a BswmdModel object, if the type is known at model generation time, the type will be the generated type. Otherwise the return type is GIParameter.

    Note: It is always allowed to call getRefTargetParameter(), also for references pointing to external types.

    All method parameters must be non-null unless documented otherwise.
